full_text: Told Alexa to play "Irish music" and the first two were from The Pogues and Van Morrison.
Playing Dropkick Murphy's "I'm Shipping Up to Boston" never disappoints.
Just watched the UEFA Champions league match between Liverpool & Benfica. The offside rule in soccer is dumb. It would be like in American football telling your WRs you can't go as deep as the DBs.
